<br>
I still prefer a high wep spec, since our wep skill as skalds are low anyway, and it affects our chances to parry.<br>
<br>
Make sure you cap your dex/str and get +11 on both wep and parry from items. STR and +wep raise your wep skill, and dex raise the chance to parry. with my spec and aug dex 2 / MoParry 2 I still parry at least once a fight unbuffed, and that can take a nasty 300 dmg off my poor 1300 unbuffed HPs <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
also make sure you cap charisma, and have BS skill at least equal to your lvl, otherwise your DD dmg range will vary more, get resisted frequently and generally do less dmg.<br>
<br>
I hope that helps<br>
